These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, havana
There 2 different types of food: kiwi, lemon
1. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the montecristo-smoker##3
2. the person eating lemon is on the right of the havana-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Cigar   | havana  | montecristo |
| Food       | kiwi | lemon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
2 different pets are kept: fish, mouse
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, surfing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
2. the owner of the mouse is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Pet   | fish | mouse |
| Sport      | surfing     | golf  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, western
There are 2 different favourite colors: aquamarine, ivory
1. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | western  |
| Color   | aquamarine | ivory |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
